Package com.genesyslab.platform.commons.connection.configuration

Class PropertyConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.genesyslab.platform.commons.connection.configuration.AbstractConnectionConfiguration
      • com.genesyslab.platform.commons.connection.configuration.PropertyConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientADDPOptions, ClientConnectionOptions, ConnectionConfiguration, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class PropertyConfiguration
extends AbstractConnectionConfiguration
implements java.io.Serializable
    The implementation of ConnectionConfiguration interface, which contains all values in java.util.Properties. It can be instantiated with any java.util.Properties instance.
